Cookies are stored in client's computer as text files and its purpose is to remember and track data pertaining to a client's usage.

Request Object contain's a cookie attribute.
It's a dictionary object of all cookie variables and their values that a client transmits.

Project-Directory
	|
	|--app/
		|
		| -- views.py
		| -- templates/
			  | -- index.html
			  | -- landing.html

To Make Cookies :

We'll use 'make_response' method to create a response object. 
Then we can use 'set_cookie' method to create the cookies.

Cookies can be used to store user statistics and etc.